; Issue: https://github.com/rustledger/rustledger/issues/223
; Description: Lot matching should work regardless of source file ordering
; Expected: No errors - lots should match even in reverse-chronological order

2000-01-01 open Assets:Abc ABC
2000-01-01 open Equity:Opening-Balances USD
2000-01-01 open Expenses:Abc USD

; Sale comes before purchase in file (reverse-chronological)
2026-01-02 * "Sale"
  Assets:Abc                                              -1 ABC {1 USD}
  Expenses:Abc

2026-01-01 * "Opening balance"
  Assets:Abc                                               1 ABC {1 USD, 2026-01-01}
  Equity:Opening-Balances
